  <summary date="2020-04-20T14:58:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Securing the National Supply Chain Act of 2020

This bill provides various tax credits related to economically distressed zones, including a tax credit based on the amount of wages paid by an employer to employees in such a zone. The bill also establishes a procedure for state and local governments to apply for designation as an economically distressed zone.</summary>
